OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FFormer Liverpool defender Steve Nicol
OL,7,Fsays it "means a great deal" to know a
OL,8,Fcollection of medals and shirts from
OL,9,Fhis career will be "appreciated for
OL,10,Fyears to come" as they prepare to go
OL,11,Funder the hammer.
OL,13,FThe items to be auctioned include
OL,14,FNicol's 1986 FA Cup winner's medal,
OL,15,Fwhich is expected to fetch between
OL,16,F#10,000 and #20,000, and a match-worn
OL,17,Fshirt from Liverpool and Everton's FA
OL,18,FCup final match in 1989.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
