FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776777070
OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FThe medal marks the first FA Cup title
OL,7,Fof the Scotsman's career, secured
OL,8,Fduring a historic 3-1 victory over
OL,9,Flocal rivals Everton at Wembley
OL,10,FStadium.
OL,12,FIt is leading the collection of
OL,13,Fmemorabilia from the former
OL,14,Ffootballer's highly successful career,
OL,15,Fwhich is set to go under the hammer at
OL,16,FPropstore auction house in London at
OL,17,Fthe end of April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776777070
OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FThe European Cup winners' medal, which
OL,7,Fwas won after Liverpool's tense 1984
OL,8,Fmatch against Roma in the Stadio
OL,9,FOlimpico in Rome, is also expected to
OL,10,Fsell for between #8,000 and #16,000.
OL,12,FThe Football Writers' Association
OL,13,F(FWA) Footballer of the Year award,
OL,14,Fwon by Nicol in 1989 for his high-
OL,15,Flevel performance at the Premier
OL,16,FLeague club, is also up for sale and
OL,17,Fis expected to fetch #2,000 to #4,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776777070
OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FOther items set to go under the hammer
OL,7,Finclude the shirt he wore during the
OL,8,FScotland v England Rous Cup game in
OL,9,F1988, which is hoped to fetch #1,000
OL,10,Fto #2,000.
OL,12,FThe auction is taking place from April
OL,13,F21 to May 14 and will also include the
OL,14,Fshirt worn by Nicol during Liverpool
OL,15,Fand Everton's FA Cup final match in
OL,16,F1989, which is expected to sell for
OL,17,F#3,000 to #6,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
