FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776777070
OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FThe 64-year-old is best known for his
OL,7,F13-year tenure at Liverpool FC, which
OL,8,Fsaw him land three FA Cup victories
OL,9,Fand score 46 goals.
OL,11,FNicol has also played for teams
OL,12,Fincluding Notts County FC, Sheffield
OL,13,FWednesday and Doncaster Rovers, and
OL,14,Femigrated to the United States in 1999
OL,15,Fto pursue a career in Major League
OL,16,FSoccer (MLS).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776777070
OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FSpeaking about the upcoming auction,
OL,7,FNicol said: "I've been fortunate to be
OL,8,Fpart of some incredible teams
OL,9,Fthroughout my career, from
OL,10,Frepresenting Scotland to my years with
OL,11,FLiverpool.
OL,13,F"These items hold many personal
OL,14,Fmemories, but I'm pleased to be
OL,15,Foffering them through Propstore, where
OL,16,Fthey'll go to fans and collectors who
OL,17,Fshare that passion for the game.
OL,19,F"It means a great deal to know they'll
OL,20,Fcontinue to be appreciated for years
OL,21,Fto come."
OL,26,@oD@MOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
