OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776777070
OL,3,CLiverpool legend's medals and shirts
OL,4,Cto be auctioned
OL,6,FThe event will offer more than 50 lots
OL,7,Favailable for worldwide bidding, with
OL,8,Fother items up for sale, including an
OL,9,FMLS all-star game shirt signed by
OL,10,Fstars including Sir David Beckham and
OL,11,FLandon Donovan.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
